      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine has a noticeable knock and several fluid leaks, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The exterior has multiple deep scratches, fading clear coat, and a dent on the rear passenger door; the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a non-functional infotainment system. This is a project car or a candidate for parts, and I strongly recommend a mechanical inspection before purchase.",
