    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute benchmark in automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of care that is rarely seen on the secondary market. Every surface, from the deep luster of the exterior finish to the immaculate, factory-fresh interior, confirms its status as a top-tier specimen. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically flawless, this is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection. This isn't just a car; it's a testament to meticulous ownership.",
      "price": 48900.0,
